1.0.0: Initial version
1.0.1: Use quaternion instead of magnetometer for direction leds
1.0.2: Fix bug with timeouts on windows (through bricklib)
1.0.3: Fix bug with ADC calibration readout (through bricklib)
1.0.4: Remove catching up of list signal messages (for chibi)
1.0.5: Fix wrong defines (see issue #1 on github)
1.0.6: Use better compass approximation
1.0.7: Add get_chip_temperature and reset function
1.0.8: Add USB hotplug support (through bricklib)
1.0.9: Set Interrupt pins to input default (otherwise they can interfere with WIFI)	
1.0.10: Change Bricklet Context size from 250 to 256 (through bricklib)
1.0.11: Return correctly from interrupt (fixes bug related to GPS Bricklet)
2.0.0: Support for protocol 2.0
2.0.1: Add watchdog timer (restart after 16s of "deadlock")
2.0.2: Add orientation calculation on/off API, make i2c communication synchronous
2.0.3: Use tick_task to detect usb connect/disconnect instead of interrupt (through bricklib)
